Sentiments.Phrase: What do you want me to say? You want a confession? Here's your confession:
Uncle Frank called in a favor, and when Uncle Frank tells you to do something, you do it, or you end up swimmin' with the fishes.
Do I regret what I’d done?
Those fellas had it coming. And the dames too.
Everyone ends up behind bars or dead eventually. I'd rather it be them than me!
So no. I don’t regret it one bit.
If I could rewind time, maybe I’d do it different.
But as it stands, we can’t rewind time...
